        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 1. — Tympanicysta stoschiana Balme from the basal Vetlugian of Nedubrovo, Vologda region; A, two vegetative cells with chloroplasts; B, vegetative cell with well-preserved chloroplast. Scale bars: 10 µm." ;
